Module project

Package payrollGUI

  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    Company
    The Company class used to hold all the employees and number of employees.
    Controller
    The Controller class is used to control the GUI.
    Date
    The Date class is used to hold a date with the variables: year, month, and day Provides easier ways to return a date for use.
    Employee
    The Employee class used to hold the profile of an employee and the payment.
    Fulltime
    The Fulltime class extends the Employee class and holds the salary and pay periods of full time employees.
    Main
    The Main class used interact with a company with the use of a GUI.
    Management
    The Management class extends the Fulltime class, holding the salary values through the role assigned.
    Month
    The Month class is used to consolidate the constant month variables used by the Date class.
    Parttime
    The Parttime class extends the Employee class.
    Profile
    The Profile class used to hold the contents of the Profile in the Employee class.
